      "options": {
        "content": "## Spend Category Summary\nItem-level spend totals grouped by APL spend category code and MCC.\nCategory codes (5A, 5D, etc.) are FIS APL purse-split identifiers from the STDFSID feed.\n**Source:** `reporting.vw_spend_category_summary` \u2192 `reporting.fact_spend_item` + `reporting.fact_spend_item_detail`\n**Audience:** Operations, Client Success, Compliance",
